lead_paragraph: Trump Entertainment Resorts Inc, which runs two casinos in Atlantic City, filed for bankruptcy protection for a third time, in another blow to the city's crumbling casino industry.

headline.main: Another Atlantic City Casino Company Files for Bankruptcy
